hom.sense:
hamozu AlX-ayoTaAni was explained by Moḥammad as meaning ‡ Madness, or insanity; syn. muwtapN, i. e. junuwnN; because it arises from the goading and pressing or pinching of the devil. (AʼObeyd, Ḳ.) 
See 1; 
